        "client_msg_id": "120fe962-5d0f-4ebd-b644-3f89028445b4",
        "text": "Here's an idea that looks easily implementable (an important condition for being able to explore it): once a thread loses activity, have it automatically copied to something like a Wiki page and send an invitation to all participants, asking them to clean it up, summarize lengthy parts, add keywords, etc.\nImplementation: a forum plus a Wiki plus a bot that links the two.",
